Kuma hakan zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka na dogon lokaci.
Willoughby, mahaifiyar yara uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance abokai na Jones da matarsa Tara Capp na shekara goma.
Willoughby ya kirkiro Truly tare da Capp a 2016 kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga kamfanin a matsayin shugaban kasa a watan Maris.
