Tsuntsaye daga Hurricane Rosa za su kawo ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yammacin Amurka
Kamar yadda aka annabta, Hurricane Rosa yana raguwa yayin da yake motsawa cikin ruwan sanyi a gabar tekun arewacin Mexico.
Duk da haka, Rosa za ta kawo ruwan sama mai ƙarfi a arewacin Mexico da kuma gabar kudu maso yammacin Amurka a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
