Wataƙila fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ya nuna a ranar Juma'a sun saurari jawabin.
Kamfanin yana lissafin matsakaicin masu sauraro a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanai ba nan da nan game da sauran tashoshin da suka watsa shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
