Jami'an tsaro shida sun ji rauni a lokacin wani hargitsi a gidan yarin maza na musamman, in ji ofishin gidan yarin.
Rikicin ya barke ne a gidan yarin Long Lartin da ke Worcestershire da misalin karfe 9:30 na safe a ranar Lahadi kuma har yanzu yana ci gaba.
An yi amfani da jami'an tsaro na musamman na Tornado don gudanar da hargitsi, wanda ya shafi fursunoni takwas kuma an tsare shi a wani ɗakin kurkuku.
An kula da jami'an a wurin da suka samu rauni a fuska.
Mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar gidan yarin ya ce: "An tura ma'aikatan gidan yarin da aka horar musamman domin su dauki matakin shawo kan wani lamari da ke faruwa a gidan yarin Long Lartin.
An kula da wasu ma'aikatan jirgin shida da suka ji rauni.
Ba mu yarda da tashin hankali a cikin gidajenmu na kurkuku ba kuma duk wanda ya aikata laifin za a kai shi ga 'yan sanda kuma za a iya yanke masa hukuncin da ya fi tsayi a kurkuku".
A kurkukun Long Lartin, akwai fursunoni fiye da 500, har da wasu daga cikin masu aikata laifi mafi tsanani a ƙasar.
A watan Yuni an sanar da cewa, an kwantar da shugaban gidan yarin a asibiti bayan wani dan fursuna ya kai masa hari.
