Shugaban ya yi magana a kaikaice game da nadin Kavanaugh yayin da yake magana game da muhimmancin samun 'yan Republican a zaben tsakiyar shekara.
"Kwanaki biyar zuwa ɗaya daga cikin zaɓe mafi muhimmanci a rayuwarmu.
Ba ni da takara, amma ina aiki sosai, in ji shi.
