Lokacin taron wani Trump West Virginia, YouTube channel
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron ne a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka dage zaben tabbatar da shi domin ya cika kujerar da ta bace a kotun koli, Trump zai nemi samar da goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar asarar iko a majalisa a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai gudana kuma ta yaya za a iya bin sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da ƙarfe 7:00 na yammacin wannan daren, Asabar, Satumba 29, 2018.
Za ku iya bin taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana ne a kan sauraron da aka yi a wannan makon na wanda zai tsaya takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai cike da tashin hankali sakamakon zargin cin zarafin mata da aka yi masa, inda aka dakatar da kuri'ar amincewa da majalisar dattawa ta yi na tsawon mako guda, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban dalilin wannan jerin kwamitocin shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba su sami wani ci gaba.
Kamfanin yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce, "waɗannan tarurruka guda biyar a mako mai zuwa na nufin karfafawa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Shugabancin majalisa na da muhimmanci sosai a kan shirinsa wanda shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke shiga lokacin kamfen", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump ga Reuters, inda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
An shirya taron na yau da dare a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling, zai iya jawo masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun labaran kafofin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh, "in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia karo na biyu a cikin wata daya, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke kan gaba a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa zai zo ya yi kokarin kara masa ƙarfi a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
