Koriya ta Arewa ta ki amincewa da rashin amincewa da makamai
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumin na kara tsananta rashin amincewar kasar a kan Amurka, wadda a irin wannan yanayi za ta ki amincewa da barin makaman nukiliyarta.
Ri Yong Ho ya bayyana a taron babban taron kungiyar ta duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki manyan matakan alheri a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, rushewar wurin gwajin nukiliya da kuma alkawarin hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga wani irin martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
