Tauraruwar Game da Karfe Kit Harington ta kai hari ga mazaunin guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin ɗan gwagwarmaya Jon Snow a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na zamanin da na Tron na Swords.
Amma dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya yi ta kai hari kan yadda ake kallon jarumin, yana mai cewa irin wannan salon a talabijin yakan sa yara su yi tunanin cewa dole ne su kasance masu taurin kai domin a girmama su.
A wata hira da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce yana ganin cewa wani abu ya ɓace kuma ya yi tunani game da yadda za a magance matsalar ƙarancin maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri ɗan wasan "Throne of Swords" mai shekara 31, ya yarda cewa wannan batun yana damunsa sosai.
'Na kaina yana damuna, sosai a yanzu - menene kuskurenmu game da namiji?' in ji shi.
'Me muka koya wa maza yayin da suke girma game da matsalar da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya kasancewa da wani ɓangare na alhakin ƙaruwar ƙarancin maza saboda halayensa masu ƙarancin maza.
Ya ci gaba: 'Menene a cikinmu, kuma menene ake koya mana?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma kan titi, da ke sa yara su yi tunanin cewa dole ne su kasance cikin wannan tsari na zama maza?
Ina tsammanin wannan shine babban ƙalubalen zamaninmu - ta yaya za mu canza abubuwa?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa wani abu ya ɓace wa matasa.'
