Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin 'yan ta'adda ta hanyar 'yan jarida
Makon daya bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka, tana tallata amfanin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yin farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi nuni da wani talla da aka biya daga China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben 'yan majalisa na Amurka da aka gudanar a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta yi watsi da shi.
Zargin da Trump ya yi game da kokarin da Beijing ke yi na shiga cikin zaben Amurka, ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne na wani yunkuri na kara matsa lamba a kan China.
Yayin da ya zama al'ada ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi talla don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin cinikayya da ke kara tsanantawa wanda ya sa suka daidaita harajin su ga kayayyakin da suke shigowa.
An yi amfani da harajin da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don cin zarafin masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, kamar yadda masana na China da na Amurka suka ce.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, in ji Branstad a wata muhawara a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, yanzu tana ƙara wa'adin ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace a jaridunmu na kyauta.
"A yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China tana amfani da ƙaunatacciyar al'adar Amurka na 'yancin magana da latsa ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A gefe guda, a cikin hirar da ake yi a kan tituna a nan Beijing, ba za ku ga masu saɓani da yawa ba, kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayoyi da yawa da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, "wani daga cikin manyan jaridu a kasar Sin ya ki amincewa da buga" labarin nasa, duk da cewa bai bayyana ko wane ne jaridar ba.
'Yan Republican suna janye mata masu zabe kafin zaben tsakiyar shekara da shari'ar Kavanaugh, manazarta sun gargadi
Da yake manyan 'yan Republican suna goyon bayan nadin Brett Kavanaugh a Kotun Koli kuma suna goyon bayansa wajen fuskantar tuhume-tuhume daban-daban na cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a ga mummunan martani, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
An yi ta-za-ka-ka-ka-ka a kan wannan batu, kuma da yawa daga cikin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna a hukumance cewa suna son su ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za ku iya janye waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa shagalin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi na minti na karshe kan binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", kamar yadda jaridar Washington, D.C., ta ruwaito Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, ta ce a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun sake maimaita taken 'November yana zuwa! a yayin zanga-zangarsu a zauren majalisar dattawa, lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zaɓi ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, kamar yadda Mic ta ruwaito.
"Himma da himmar 'yan Democrat na tashi sama", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa mai zaman kansa, a shafin yanar gizo na labarai.
Mutane suna cewa sun riga sun yi tsayi; gaskiya ne.
Amma za su iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin masu zaɓen da ke cikin yankunan karkara da kuma matasa masu zaɓe, tsakanin shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda sau da yawa ba sa jefa ƙuri'a duk da cewa ba sa son shugaban.
Tun kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a fili, inda ya ba da cikakkun bayanai game da zargin cin zarafin da ya yi wa dan takarar kotun koli, manazarta sun yi hasashen cewa za a iya samun mummunar amsa idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da shi.
"GOP ta zama wani abu mai rikitarwa", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun batun jefa kuri'a a kwamitin ba ne, ko kuma ko za a jefa Kavanaugh a benci, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka gudanar da lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat.
Ko yaya dai, jama'ar Amirka sun nuna sun rabu tsakanin wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da karamin kashi na goyon bayan na karshe.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce haka game da Ford.
Bayan nacewar Flake, FBI tana gudanar da bincike kan zargin da Ford ya yi, da kuma akalla daya daga cikin masu tuhumar, Deborah Ramirez, kamar yadda jaridar The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ya shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari a lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta ce dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a lokacin da take bikin a lokacin da take karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin fara sabuwar intanet domin kalubalantar Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, yana kaddamar da wani kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin karshe na almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ya samo asali daga dandalin bude tushen Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da abin da mutane za su iya samun dama da kuma wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azin cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce ta mallaki duniya.
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar  kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi ko POD.
Za su iya haɗa da jerin lambobin sadarwa, abubuwan da za a yi, kalandarku, littattafan kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sana'a da na mutum.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne ke iya zaɓan wane irin bayani ne zai samu.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafa kai ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar John Bruce, Shugaba na kamfanin, shi ne samar da isassun albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma basira don tabbatar da cewa kowa yana iya samun damar amfani da Solid.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da aka saya daga IBM, wasu masu haɓaka a cikin ma'aikatan da aka ɗauka don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'umma na masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a duk duniya za su iya samar da nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su gaya wa Facebook da Google ko su gabatar da sauyi na gaba daya ba inda tsarin kasuwancin su ya lalace gaba daya daga dare.
"Ba ma neman izininsu".
A wani rubutu a kan Medium da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka gina daga Solid".
A 1994 Berners-Lee ya sauya intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko bayan kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da Shugaba na World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: An ambaci limamin yakin duniya da Victoria Cross
An tuna da limamin Cocin Ingila guda daya da aka ba lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko a matsayin mai yaki a garinsa bayan shekaru 100.
Lt. Col, Reverend Bernard Vann, ya samu wannan girmamawa a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba, 1918 a harin da aka kai a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi, kuma bai san cewa ya sami matsayi mafi girma a ƙasar Britaniya ba.
A ranar Asabar a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire, jikokinsa biyu sun kaddamar da wani allon tunawa.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce abin "alamar ne sosai" cewa za a buɗe dutsen daidai shekaru 100 bayan nasarar da kakansa ya yi.
A cewar jaridar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba na shekara ta 1918 Laftanar Janar Van ya jagoranci rundunarsa a kan Canal Saint-Quentin  ta hanyar hazo mai zafi, a ƙarƙashin wuta mai nauyi na sansanin da na'urorin yaki.
