Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji cewa shi 'yar kasa ne saboda jima'i
Tom Daley mai iyo a gasar Olympics ya ce ya girma yana jin kasa da kowa saboda jima'i - amma wannan ya ba shi dalili na samun nasara.
Dan shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa "ba kowa bane kamar ni" ba har sai da ya kai makarantar sakandare.
Da yake magana a shirin farko na shirin Desert Island Discs na Radio 4, wanda Lauren Laverne ta gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin 'yan luwadi don ba da "bege" ga wasu.
Ya kuma ce zama uba ya sa ya daina damuwa da cin gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin Kirsty Young ta ɗauki hutun watanni da yawa don rashin lafiya.
Da yake gabatar da kansa a matsayin mai tsattsauran ra'ayi a cikin shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya bayyana cewa ya ji "kasa da kowa" yayin da yake girma saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba cewa yana son yara maza da mata".
Ya ce, "Yau, jin kasa da ni, da kuma jin banbanci, su ne abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfi da kuzari na yi nasara".
Ta ce tana son ta tabbatar da cewa ita wani abu ce, don kada ta sa kowa baƙin ciki idan suka gano cewa ita mace ce.
Gwarzon dan wasan Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da fuskarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Australia don yin kira ga kasashe da yawa da su dakatar da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi magana ne domin yana jin cewa yana da sa'a ya rayu a fili ba tare da sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba da "bege" ga wasu.
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce, ya yi mamakin yadda ya yi soyayya da wani mutum - darektan fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a 2013.
Daley ya auri wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar, wanda ya girme shi da shekara 20 a bara, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da ya sha wahala sosai tun yana saurayi" - ya halarci wasannin Olympics na farko yana ɗan shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji bayan shekaru uku - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya wanda ya sha irin wannan tashin hankali da rashin lafiya.
Sun zama iyayen wani yaro a watan Yuni mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "dukkanin tunaninsa ya canja".
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da ya shafi shi ne cewa dole ne in lashe lambar zinare", in ji shi.
Ka san, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
Na lashe lambar zinare ta gasar Olympics Robbie ne.
Sunan ɗansa ya yi kama da na mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40 bayan an gano shi da cutar kansa ta kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa yana mutuwa ba, kuma abu na karshe da ya tambaye shi shi ne ko suna da tikitin zuwa London 2012 - domin yana son ya zauna a gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba" "Ba za ka kasance a nan ba don ka kasance a gaba, baba", in ji shi.
"Ina riƙe da hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi, kuma har sai da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu, ban fahimci cewa ba shi da nasara ba", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa Daley ya yi gasa a wasannin Olympics na 2012, inda ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa abin da na yi mafarki a rayuwata shi ne yin iyo a gaban jama'a a wasannin Olympics, babu wani abin da ya fi wannan", in ji shi.
Wannan kuma ya ba da shawarar zaɓin waƙar sa ta farko - Girman Heather Small - wanda ke da ma'ana ta musamman a gare shi a cikin shirye-shiryen wasannin Olympics kuma har yanzu yana sa shi jin daɗin fata.
An gabatar da shirin Desert Island Discs a BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na BST.
Mickelson da ba shi da kyau ya tsaya a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa wani tarihi a ranar Lahadi lokacin da zai buga wasan Ryder Cup na 47 amma dole ne ya dawo cikin koshin lafiya domin ya guji zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ya buga wasan na shekara biyu a karon 12 da aka yi, ya samu kwantar da hankali daga kyaftin din Jim Furyk domin wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu a ranar Asabar.
