Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A cewar majiyoyin hukuma, akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia ranar Juma'a.
An katse sadarwa kuma jami'an agaji ba su samu wani bayani ba daga yankin Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu da ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
Bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 daga Palu.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kusa da bakin tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma yana da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka shafa, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala yanki ne wanda ya kai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 miles) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, Regency, yanki ne na yanki wanda ke da alhakin lardi, yana da mazaunan kusan 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samar da tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya da musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Har ila yau, hakar nickel babban aiki ne a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya afkawa yankin yammacin Donggala a 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin girgizar ƙasa da ake kira Pacific Fire Belt kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi ƙarfi da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin mutanen da ke Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya bugi gabar tekun kudu inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
