An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakiyar shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, bisa zargin kai hari.
A ranar Asabar ne rundunar 'yan sanda ta jihar Alaska ta ba da sanarwar cewa an kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga garin Wasilla, a jihar Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma hana shi kai karar da kuma tsayayya da kama shi.
Rahoton ya ce, sa'ad da wata da ta san shi ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta kai rahoton laifin da ake zarginsa da aikata laifi, sai ya ƙwace wayar daga hannunta.
An kai Palin zuwa Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an kafa belinsa a kan $500, kamar yadda KTUU ta ruwaito.
A cewar gidan talabijin, ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar kuma ya bayyana cewa "ba shi da laifi".
Za a iya tuhumar Palin da laifuffuka uku na farko, wato, a ɗaure shi har shekara guda kuma a ci tararsa $250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifi na biyu wanda ake iya hukuntawa da kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala dubu biyu.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka tuhumi Palin da aikata laifuka ba.
A watan Disamba na shekara ta 2017, an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton harin.
Yanzu haka, ana shari'ar a Kotun Tsofaffin Sojoji na Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da cin zarafin cikin gida, da hana sanar da laifin, da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Yarinyar da yake so ta yi masa zargin cewa ya buge ta da hannu a fuska.
Kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji sun soki Sarah Palin a 2016 saboda danganta halayyar ɗanta mai tashin hankali da ciwon damuwa na bayan-tashin hankali wanda ya biyo bayan lokacin da ta yi a Iraki.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Mutane Daruruwa Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasar mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta jawo tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
Wutar lantarki da na sadarwa ba su da aiki kuma adadin wadanda suka mutu zai ƙaru a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya wanda ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Bidiyo na nuna lokacin da aka yi ambaliyar sun bazu a shafukan sada zumunta.
Sa'ad da tsunami ya afka bakin teku, daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin a bakin teku a birnin Palu.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wadanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara na New York suna neman a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ya kai harin ta'addanci wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba tun 1953 saboda wani laifi na tarayya.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don yin hargitsi a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a yankin Lower Manhattan inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a watan Oktoba.
Bisa ga sharuddan neman hukuncin kisa a karamar hukumar New York, don a tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe "da gangan" kuma ya yi wa wasu mutane rauni mai tsanani.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, duka waɗannan zarge-zarge na iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, babban alkalin kotun tarayya ya zargi Saipov da laifuka 22, da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da ke hade da aikata laifi, wanda ake amfani da shi a cikin shari'o'in da ake gudanarwa da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya, da kuma laifuka guda daya na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsarin da aka yi da gangan", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin "mai banƙyama, mai zalunci da lalata".
Sanarwar ta ce "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa iyalan da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco lahani, zargi da kuma asarar rai".
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe 'yan yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Ajantina.
Shekaru goma sun shige tun lokacin da aka yi shari'ar kisa na ƙarshe a gundumar Kudancin New York.
An tuhumi mutumin da ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin ɗaurin rai da rai a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
An kashe shi a karo na karshe a New York a 1953 a kan shari'ar tarayya na Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, miji da mata da aka zarge da yin makirci ta hanyar leken asiri da kuma sanya su a kan laifin ba da bayanai ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Ma'auratan Rosenberg sun mutu a kan kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, Saipov, ɗan Uzbekistan, bai nuna alamar tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya yi alfahari da abin da ya yi a gaban masu binciken.
A cewar masu tuhumar, Saipov ya gaya wa hukumomi cewa ya yanke shawarar kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
Ya kuma nemi 'yan sanda su rataye tutar ISIS a dakinsa na asibiti.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin masu ba da shawara na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "a bayyane yake ya yi takaici" da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukunci da hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da wata damar sakewa ba zai kara tsawaita raunin da abubuwan suka haifar ga duk wadanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar masu kare Saipov ta riga ta roki masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin Tory ya ce dole ne NIGEL FARAGE ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "karfafa rundunar jama'a" a wani zanga-zanga a taron Tory a yau.
Lokacin da wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ya kula da tattaunawar da Tarayyar Turai, tsohon shugaban Jam'iyyar 'Yancin Birtaniya ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba" daga masu shakkar kudin Turai.
A watan Maris, Peter Bone dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "za ta riga ta fita daga Turai" idan Farage ne Sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta wajen kokarin sulhunta matsayin jam'iyyarta mai cike da rarrabuwa an nuna su ne a wajen 'yan Tory masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a Turai da suka halarci wani gangamin nuna rashin amincewa da Brexit a London.
Firayim Minista na kokarin aiwatar da shirin Chequers a tsakanin hare-haren masu goyon bayan Brexit, wadanda suke son zama a Turai da kuma Tarayyar Turai.
Aminai sun nace da ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da tsananin tashin hankali da ake samu, da kuma tilasta wa masu shakkar kudin Turai da kuma 'yan jam'iyyar Labour su zabi tsakanin abin da May ke bayarwa da kuma "hargitsi".
A taron Leave Means Leave da aka yi a Solihull, Bone ya ce yana son ya yi watsi da shirin Chequers.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a ba Farage aikin gudanar da tattaunawar da Brussels.
"Zamu riga mun fita daga Turai a yanzu", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Ina goyon bayan Brexit amma dole ne mu yi watsi da shirin Chequers".
Da yake bayyana dalilan da suka sa ya yi adawa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya ba domin mu zama masu hidima.
Muna son mu yi amfani da dokokinmu a ƙasarmu".
Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayin cewa ra'ayin jama'a zai canza tun lokacin zaben 2016, "ra'ayin cewa 'yan Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su kasance a Turai ba gaskiya ba ne".
'Yar majalisa Tory Andrea Jenkyns, mai goyon bayan Brexit, ta halarci gangamin kuma ta gaya wa manema labarai: "Ina gaya wa Firayim Minista kawai ya saurari mutane.
Shirin Chequers ba shi da kyau ga jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su yi zabe a kansa ba, kuma ba su da goyon bayan jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutukar neman zabe da ke zagayawa tituna don su ba mu damar yin zabe.
Ka daina wannan shirin na Chequers ka fara sauraro".
A cikin wani sako mai cike da ma'ana ga May, ya kara da cewa: "Firaministoci na iya riƙe mukamin su idan sun cika alkawuransu".
A taron, Farage ya ce ya kamata 'yan siyasa su iya "jin matsin lamba" idan suna son su ci amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Yanzu batun amincewa ne tsakaninmu, jama'a, da kuma siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma mun zo nan ne mu gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari su yi hakan ba".
A cikin wani sako ga taron masu farin ciki ya kara da cewa: "Ina son ku ji matsin lamba a kan 'yan siyasarmu da ke gab da cin amanar Brexit.
Za mu tattara sojojin jama'ar kasar nan da suka kada kuri'ar ficewar Birtaniya daga EU, kuma ba za mu daina ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai zaman kanta, mai cin gashin kanta da alfahari".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a Turai sun yi tafiya a kan titunan Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya kaɗan ne suka tura Tories a kan tutar Brexit bayan an kafa kungiyar a karshen mako.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta yi wa 'yan Conservatives ba'a game da matsalar tsaro da suka fuskanta da wata manhajar jam'iyyar a taron buɗe taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne da suke cewa za su iya kafa tsarin IT da dukan fasaha don yarjejeniyar Canada da ƙari, don iyakoki marasa rikici da kuma cinikayya mara iyaka a Ireland", in ji shi.
Wannan abin dariya ne.
Babu wani Brexit mai kyau", in ji shi.
