Ƙungiyar Elite League: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun murmure bayan shan kashi a ranar Juma'a a wasan Elite League da suka yi da Belfast Giants inda suka ci wasan dawowa da ci 5-3 a ranar Asabar a Dundee.
Giants sun yi nasara da kwallaye biyu a raga a kan Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kai 'yan wasan gida a kan gungumen azaba kafin Dwyer ya mayar da Giants a gaba.
Francois Bouchard ya ci wa Dundee kwallo kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci biyu ya sa suka ci.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da 'yan Adam Keefe suka sha kaye a gasar Elite League, inda suka yi nasara da Dundee da ci 2-1.
Kungiyoyin biyu sun riga sun hadu sau hudu a wannan kakar kuma Giants sun ci wasanni uku na farko.
Dwyer ya zira kwallaye na farko a minti na 3:35 a kan taimako na Kendall McFaull, yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka bayan minti huɗu a kan taimako na David Rutherford.
A wani wasa da ya yi da farko, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gida a cikin wasa a minti na 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya ba da taimakon daidaitawa ga Cownie a minti na 15:16.
Dwyer ya yi wa Giants nasara da ci na biyu a wasan da aka yi a ƙarshen rabin wasan.
'Yan wasan gida sun sake yin wasa, kuma Bouchard ya sake samun daidaito bayan wani dabarun da aka yi a minti na 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun taimaka wa Nielsen wanda ya jagoranci Dundee a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen rabin lokaci kuma ya yi shelar nasarar tawagarsa ta hanyar zura kwallo ta biyar a tsakiyar rabin lokaci.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su buga wasansu na gaba a Milton Keynes ranar Juma'a.
