Ma'auratan sun musanta cewa su masu wariyar launin fata ne, suna kwatanta wannan bukatar da "cin hanci da rashawa".
Lynsey Plasco-Flaxman, mahaifiyar yara biyu, ta nuna bacin ranta lokacin da ta gano cewa sabuwar mai renon yara, Giselle Maurice, ta zo ranar farko ta aiki a 2016, baƙar fata ce.
