Amma maimakon ta aika wa mijinta, sai ta aika wa Miss Maurice, sau biyu.
Jaridar New York Post ta ce bayan ta fahimci kuskuren, "mai kunya" Mrs. Plasco-Flaxman ta kori Miss Maurice ta ce ba ta ji daɗin tsohuwar mai renon ba, Ba'amurke, kuma tana tsammanin wani ɗan Filipin ne.
