Ta yaya yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya amfanar Beijing
An yi gagarumar nasara a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma yayin da yakin bai gama ba, masana sun ce bambancin da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya riga ya ba da gargadi na farko a wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya faru ne a wannan makon tare da sabon haraji kan kayayyaki masu darajar sama da dala biliyan 200 (euro biliyan 175) wanda ke nufin cewa za a sanya haraji kan rabin kayayyakin da suka fito daga China.
A duk lokacin da aka kai hari, Beijing ta yi irin wannan matakin ne ta hanyar saka haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma a kan dala biliyan 60 na kayayyakin Amurka.
China ta yi alkawarin mayar wa Amurka da martani, kuma ba zai yiwu ba da sauri tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ya koma baya.
Don Washington ta yi watsi da wannan, dole ne ta yi biyayya ga bukatun Amurka, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da kyau, matsin lamba na yakin cinikayya da Amurka na iya yin tasiri mai kyau a kan China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani mataki na siyasa da aka ɗauka da sauri daga Washington ko kuma Beijing zai iya kafa yanayi na farko na rushewar tattalin arziki a ƙasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda aka sani a yanzu", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike a Asiya a Cibiyar Bincike don Sabuwar Tsaro ta Amirka.
Syria ta "shirya" don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, in ji ministan harkokin wajen kasar
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina kasar da ta girgiza bayan yaki na shekaru bakwai.
A gaban babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau, yanayin da ke ƙasar ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaƙi da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da al'amuran al'umma cikin sauki.
Yanzu akwai dukkan yanayi don 'yan gudun hijira su koma ƙasarsu da son rai, waɗanda suka bar ƙasarsu saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe ɗaya da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka gudu daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya fara a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da har yanzu suke zaune a Syria suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yarda da taimakon da za a ba ta don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai yarda da wani taimako ba tare da wani sharadi ko daga kasashen da suka goyi bayan tawayen.
Turai ta ci gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Teamungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta doke Team USA tare da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 17.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a wajen Paris, Faransa.
A sakamakon haka, Amirka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a Turai, kuma ba ta ci gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin ne lokacin da tawagar kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Gwarzon dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa tee-shot dinsa cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na wasan, inda ya baiwa Francesco Molinari nasara.
Dan wasan Italiya ya yi fice a duk wasanninsa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka taba samun ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sha kashi da maki 5&4 daga dan wasan Denmark Thorbjorn Olesen na tawagar Turai.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowa a duniya, ya ci 2 da 1 ga dan wasan Ingila Ian Poulter wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
Wani tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup, Sergio Garcia na Spain wanda ya yi wasanni takwas, ya zama dan wasan Turai da ya fi kowacce nasara a tarihin gasar da maki 25.5.
"A kullum ba na kuka, amma a yau ina kuka.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki da na sake lashe kofin.
Wannan nasara ce ta tawagar kuma ina farin cikin cewa na bayar da gudummawata", in ji Garcia mai farin ciki bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da shaida ga ɗan ƙasarsa John Ram wanda ya doke almara na golf na Amurka Tiger Woods da ƙimar 2 da 1 a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Lahadi.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce, "Idan na yi tunanin cewa na girma ne ta kallon wasansa, ina alfahari da na doke Tiger Woods.
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu jimlar wasanninsa a gasar Ryder Cup ya kai 13 da 21 da 3 da aka yi wasa.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki idan ka yi la'akari da cewa shi ne daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci, ya lashe 14 daga cikin manyan wasannin, na biyu kawai ga Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi ta neman hanyoyin zuwa gasar a duk karshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf a matakin farko a gasar.
Kyaftin din Amurka Jim Furyk ya ce bayan wasan da tawagarsa ta yi: "Ina alfahari da waɗannan yara domin sun yi yaƙi.
A wani lokaci a safiyar yau mun matsa wa tawagar Turai.
Mun yi hasarar wannan dama.
Ka ba Thomas yabo.
Babban kyaftin ne.
Dukan 'yan wasansa 12 sun yi kyau sosai.
Zan yi aiki da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin gasar Ryder kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan yara 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftinansu.
Mun yi duk abin da za mu iya.
Amma sun fi mu wasa".
Sabuntawar jan ruwa: Rashin ruwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin Daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa, a wasu wurare a yankin Tampa Bay, ruwan sama mai ruwan sama yana raguwa sosai.
FWC ta ce, yanayin fure-fure, wanda ke nuna raguwar maida hankali, ya bayyana a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier.
Furewar jan ruwa tana kaiwa kusan mil 130 na gabar teku daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudancin Lee County.
An gano wuraren da ke da nisan mil 10 daga yankin Hillsborough amma a yankuna da yawa fiye da na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da jan ruwa a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an samu matsakaicin taro a Pinellas County ko kuma a gabar tekun, matsakaicin taro daga low zuwa high a Hillsborough County, daga low zuwa high a Manatee County, daga low zuwa high a Sarasota County ko kuma a gabar tekun, daga low zuwa middle a Charlotte County, daga low zuwa high a Lee County ko kuma a gabar tekun, da kuma low a Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahoton cututtukan numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a samu wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba.
